---
description: AI and Gemini usage rules
globs: lib/**/*.{ts,tsx},agents/**/*.{ts,tsx},prompts/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

Follow `AI_RULES.md` and `PROMPT_ENGINEERING.md`.

- Model: `gemini-2.5-flash` via `lib/gemini.ts`.
- Use template IDs from `prompts/registry.ts` via `resolveTemplate()` / `buildAgentPromptBundle()`.
- Use `generateStructuredResponse` with Zod for JSON outputs.
- No prompts inside components.
- Do not send secrets or service keys to the model.
